 9. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
10. the person who likes pink is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
12. the person playing domino is not to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##8
13. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ivory##5
14. the person who likes emerald is the person eating peas##1
15. the person who likes ivory is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##8
16. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the person who likes ivory##8
